<DocsLayout title="Terraform вҖ” GCP">
  <h1>Terraform вҖ” GCP</h1>
  <p>
    The GCP Terraform module deploys EncodeSwarmr on Google Cloud Platform using Compute Engine for the controller
    and a Managed Instance Group for agents, Cloud SQL for PostgreSQL, Filestore for shared media storage, and a
    regional HTTP(S) and TCP load balancer.
  </p>

