  <p>Use Spot (preemptible) VMs for agents with <code>agent_use_spot = true</code> to reduce agent costs by up to 80%.</p>

  <h2>Cleanup</h2>
  <pre><code># Destroy all resources
terraform destroy

# If Filestore deletion is blocked by NFS mounts:
gcloud filestore instances delete encodeswarmr-media \
  --zone=us-central1-a \
  --project=my-project-id</code></pre>
